::Grounded::
Grounded let all his memory's of the past slip for now. He walked out of 
the CR.
"Burning Hammer." he called out. Although he was now blind he could tell 
where things were through vibrations in ground and air as well as 
sounds. "I was the one that suggested the memory deletion, but only 
because i though of you as someone I would hate to lose. Trinity is 
right here. You were like her best friend.  What is money, when you are 
stuck here anyways.  With us, you have always been rich."
